---
name: v21-native-binder-match-guard
---

```scalascript
def classify(n: Int): String = n match
  case x if x < 0  => "negative"
  case 0            => "zero"
  case x if x < 10 => "small"
  case _            => "large"

println(classify(-3))
println(classify(0))
println(classify(7))
println(classify(42))
```
